column2: Initiating, pioneering energy. Independent, bold, courageous, assertive, fiery, inspirational, direct, decisive. Can be egotistical, impulsive, impatient, aggressive, and lack subtlety.

Stable and enduring, defined by strong values and an unyielding, earthy nature with acquisitive tendencies and powerful desires. At times, may be perceived as rigid, stubborn, overly possessive, or self-indulgent.
Agile, versatile, and inquisitive, characterized by a fluid and conversational style with many ideas. Can exhibit volatility, superficiality, inconsistency, and restlessness.
Nurturing, protective, and tenacious, with pronounced emotional sensitivity and deeply rooted foundations. At times, may be overly protective, reluctant to let go, timid, or reclusive.
Self-confident, generous, and warm-hearted, with strong leadership qualities and a dramatic presence. May occasionally appear overly proud, vain, extravagant, or arrogant.
Meticulous, discriminating, and practical, marked by a focus on health and hard work. Can sometimes be hypercritical, petty, or perfectionistic.
Even-handed, harmonious, and artistic, with a diplomatic manner and a strong sense of fairness. May at times be overcompromising, excessively appeasing, or judgmental.
Intense and magnetic, possessing a penetrating perception and the capacity to confront challenges head on. Can display destructive tendencies, vengefulness, jealousy, or excessive drama.
Inspiring, with a broad vision, enthusiasm, and goal-seeking drive. Truthfulness and adventurousness define the approach; however, recklessness, lack of restraint, or tactlessness may also emerge.

Disciplined, responsible, and reliable, displaying industrious, conscientious, and practical traits that foster achievement. Nonetheless, tendencies toward pessimism, conventionality, rigidity, materialism, or callousness may be evident.

Humanitarian and innovative with a strong group orientation and progressive drive to serve others. In some cases, rebellious, eccentric, aloof, emotionally superficial, or overly extroverted behaviors may appear.
Compassionate, sensitive, self-sacrificing, gentle, and intuitive. Yet, escapism, impracticality, hypersensitivity, or gullibility may sometimes occur.
